  "title": "Site Supervisor",
  "description": "<h2><u>Site Supervisor</u></h2>\n<p>Responsibilities:<br>\nMonitor and supervise roll-on-site works and any other construction-related activities.<br>\nCoordinate sub-contractors and resources, including workers and machinery on site.<br>\nTo ensure delivered construction materials are of specified requirements.<br>\nPrepare daily site reports, take site progress pictures, check and take site measurements.<br>\nMinimise material and manpower wastage.<br>\nHandle labour and supplier disputes<br>\n<br>\nJob Requirements:<br>\nStrong technical knowledge and capability to solve technical and site issues<br>\nCheck daily attendance of workers<br>\nAttend site meetings with site agent &amp; sub-contractors.<br>\nStrong communication skills</p>\n<p><br></p>",
